'''R4-D2''' was one of two [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]] owned by a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] named [[Darrus Jeht/Legends|Darrus Jeht]]. The other [[Droid/Legends|droid]] was called [[R4-D1]]. Both droids were used aboard a [[Delta-6 Sprite-class starfighter|Delta-6 starfighter]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. R4-D2 and his companion often provided more input data than the ship's flight computer could handle, causing instabilities at the worst of times. Both droids also tended to argue with each other over their input, causing more problems.

